documents.text: Our return policy allows customers to return items within 30 days of purchase. All items must be in original condition with tags attached. Refunds will be processed within 5-7 business days after we receive the returned item. For defective items, we offer free return shipping.

We offer several shipping options: Standard shipping (5-7 business days) for $5.99, Express shipping (2-3 business days) for $12.99, and Overnight shipping (1 business day) for $24.99. Free standard shipping is available on orders over $50.

Customer service is available Monday through Friday from 9 AM to 6 PM EST. You can contact us via email at support@ecommerce.com, phone at 1-800-SHOP-NOW, or live chat on our website. We respond to emails within 24 hours.

Our size guide helps you find the perfect fit. For clothing: XS (0-2), S (4-6), M (8-10), L (12-14), XL (16-18). For shoes: we offer sizes 5-12 in both standard and wide widths. Measurements should be taken without clothing for accuracy.

We offer a 1-year warranty on all electronic items and a 90-day warranty on clothing and accessories. Warranty covers manufacturing defects but does not cover damage from normal wear and tear or misuse.
Payment methods accepted include all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover), PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and buy-now-pay-later options through Klarna and Afterpay.

Frequently Asked Questions: Q: Can I track my order? A: Yes, you'll receive a tracking number via email once your order ships. Q: Do you offer gift wrapping? A: Yes, gift wrapping is available for $3.99.

Return Shipping Costs: For defective, damaged, or incorrect items shipped to you, we provide free return shipping labels via email. For returns due to personal preference, wrong size selection, or change of mind, customers are responsible for return shipping costs. Standard return shipping costs $5.99 via ground service.

Return Status Tracking: Track your return status by logging into your account and visiting the Returns section, or use your return confirmation number on our returns page. You will receive email notifications when: 1) We receive your returned item, 2) Your return is approved/rejected, 3) Your refund is processed. Customer service can also provide status updates at 1-800-SHOP-NOW.

Rejected Returns: If your return is rejected, we will email you with the specific reason (e.g., item condition, missing tags, outside return window). The item will be shipped back to you at no additional cost. In some cases, we may offer store credit as an alternative. You can appeal the decision by contacting customer service within 5 days.

Canceling Return Requests: You can cancel a return request within 24 hours of submission if you have not yet shipped the item. Contact customer service immediately. Once the item is shipped back to us, the return cannot be cancelled. However, if you change your mind after shipping, you can decline the refund when we contact you, and we will return the item to you free of charge.
